0.80:
* Updated english version of man page: added more info about -S option
  (described status information fields, added note about possible last
  password change date imprecision) and exit codes.
* Updated translations.
* Auditing fixes.
* Minor bug fixes.
0.79:
* Dropped the rpm spec file.  Conceptually it belongs in distributions,
  and two-way synchronization between fedorahosted and Fedora pkgs repository
  doesn't really make sense.
* Updated man page, notably adding long option formats.
* Updated translations.
* Very minor bug fixes.
* Build system and warning cleanups.
* libuser >= 0.58 is now required.
